    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571734,
    "reference_id": 124394,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶大和便雅憫的敵人說他們已經向耶和華（雅巍）獻祭多久了？</strong></p><p>猶大和便雅憫的敵人說，自從亞述王以撒哈頓的時代以來，他們一直在向耶和華（雅巍）獻祭。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:2",
          "end_ref": "15004002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571735,
    "reference_id": 124395,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:4–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004004-15004005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>那地的人對猶大人做了什麼？</strong></p><p>那地的人使猶大人的手發軟，使他們不敢建造，且又雇謀士對付他們，使他們的計劃落空。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:4",
          "end_ref": "15004005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571736,
    "reference_id": 124396,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>這地的百姓使猶大人的手軟弱，並使他們懼怕建造，又雇用謀士來破壞他們的計劃，這樣持續了多久呢？</strong></p><p>那地的人民對猶大人民這樣做是從波斯王塞魯士年間，直到波斯王大流士的統治為止。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:5",
          "end_ref": "15004005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571737,
    "reference_id": 124397,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶大和便雅憫的敵人在亞哈隨魯統治之初寫了什麼？</strong></p><p>在亞哈隨魯統治之初，敵人寫了一份控告猶大和耶路撒冷居民的書信。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:6",
          "end_ref": "15004006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571738,
    "reference_id": 124398,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>敵人告訴王關於耶路撒冷的什麼事？</strong></p><p>敵人跟王說耶路撒冷是個反叛的城市。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:12",
          "end_ref": "15004012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571739,
    "reference_id": 124399,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>在敵人寄給王的信被宣讀後，王做了什麼？</strong></p><p>在敵人寄給王的信被宣讀後，王下令查閱記錄，要看敵人所寫的關於耶路撒冷過去的叛亂歷史是否屬實。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:19",
          "end_ref": "15004019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571740,
    "reference_id": 124400,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 4:24",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15004024",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>在耶路撒冷建造神的殿的工作停止了多久？</strong></p><p>在耶路撒冷建造神的殿的工作停止，直到波斯王大流士統治的第二年。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15004024",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:24",
          "end_ref": "15004024",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 4:24"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571741,
    "reference_id": 124401,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 5:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15005001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>先知哈該和撒迦利亞做了什麼？</strong></p><p>他們奉以色列神的名，向在猶大和耶路撒冷的猶太人說預言。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15005001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:1",
          "end_ref": "15005001",
