    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571745,
    "reference_id": 124405,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 5:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15005012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼天上的神將猶大人的列祖交在巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒的手中？</strong></p><p>天上的神將猶大人交在巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒的手中，是因為他們的列祖犯罪而激怒了祂。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15005012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:12",
          "end_ref": "15005012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571746,
    "reference_id": 124406,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 5:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15005014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>塞魯士王給了省長設巴薩哪些物品？</strong></p><p>塞魯士王將原本屬於神殿裡的金、銀器皿拿來，交給設巴薩。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15005014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:14",
          "end_ref": "15005014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571747,
    "reference_id": 124407,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 5:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15005015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>塞魯士王命令設巴薩如何處理屬於神殿的金、銀器皿？</strong></p><p>塞魯士王命令設巴薩將金、銀器皿帶走，並將它們存放在位於耶路撒冷的神殿中。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15005015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:15",
          "end_ref": "15005015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571748,
    "reference_id": 124408,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 5:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15005017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>達乃和示他‧波斯乃及其同黨要求王做什麼？</strong></p><p>他們要求王察看府庫，看塞魯士是否曾下令在耶路撒冷建造神的殿。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15005017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:17",
          "end_ref": "15005017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 5:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571749,
    "reference_id": 124409,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><span><strong>大流士王是如何回應那關於看察塞</strong></span><strong>魯士王</strong><span><strong>是否曾下令，要在耶路撒冷建造神殿的這個請求的？</strong></span></p><p><span>大流士王降旨，命人搜查巴比倫府庫中的書卷，看塞</span>魯士<span>王是否曾下旨在耶路撒冷建造神的殿。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:1",
          "end_ref": "15006001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571750,
    "reference_id": 124410,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當王大流士下令在巴比倫的檔案館中進行搜索時，發現了什麼？</strong></p><p>他在米底亞省的亞馬他的宮中發現了一卷書卷。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:2",
          "end_ref": "15006002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571751,
    "reference_id": 124411,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>塞魯士王在他作王的第一年做了什麼？</strong></p><p>塞魯士王頒布了一項關於在耶路撒冷神的殿的法令。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:3",
          "end_ref": "15006003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571752,
    "reference_id": 124412,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>根據塞魯士王的法令，建造耶路撒冷神殿的費用應如何支付？</strong></p><p>建造在耶路撒冷神的殿的費用將由王庫支付。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:4",
          "end_ref": "15006004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571753,
    "reference_id": 124413,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>根據塞魯士王的法令，什麼應該被帶回神的殿？</strong></p><p>根據塞魯士王的法令，尼布甲尼撒曾帶到巴比倫的屬於耶路撒冷神的殿的金、銀器皿，都應該被帶回耶路撒冷神的殿。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:5",
          "end_ref": "15006005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571754,
    "reference_id": 124414,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>在大流士王閱讀了塞魯士王的法令後，大流士王寫信給達乃、示他‧波斯乃及他們的同黨，吩咐他們，他們應該要怎麼做那關於在耶路撒冷所進行的建造神的殿的工作呢？</strong></p><p>大流士王命令達乃和示他‧波斯乃及他們的同黨，不要干涉神的殿的工作，並要遠離它，以便神的殿能夠順利建造。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:7",
          "end_ref": "15006007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571755,
    "reference_id": 124415,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼塞魯士說，他希望給猶太人提供建造神的殿所需的一切？</strong></p><p>塞魯士說，他希望給猶大人提供他們所需的一切來建造神的殿，這樣猶大人就可以向天上的神獻上馨香的祭，並為王和他的兒子的生命禱告。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:10",
          "end_ref": "15006010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571756,
    "reference_id": 124416,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:11",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006011",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>大流士王降旨表示那些改變王的命令的人會如何？</strong></p><p>大流士王降旨，<span>無論是誰更改這命令，必從他房屋中拆出一根樑來，把他舉起並懸在其上，又使他的房屋成為糞堆。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006011",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:11",
          "end_ref": "15006011",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:11"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571757,
    "reference_id": 124417,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>哈該和撒迦利亞如何協助猶大長老們重建聖殿的工作？</strong></p><p>哈該和撒迦利亞<span>藉著說預言，幫助猶大人的長老們順利進行重建聖殿的工作。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:14",
          "end_ref": "15006014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571758,
    "reference_id": 124418,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>重建聖殿的工作是於何時完成的？</strong></p><p>重建聖殿的工作是在大流士王統治的第六年，亞達月的第三天完成的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:15",
          "end_ref": "15006015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571759,
    "reference_id": 124419,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>祭司和利未人為誰宰殺逾越節的羊羔？</strong></p><p><span>祭司和利未人為一切被擄歸回之人、為他們的弟兄們、祭司們，以及為自己宰殺逾越節的羊羔。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:20",
          "end_ref": "15006020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571760,
    "reference_id": 124420,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 6:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15006022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼猶大人歡歡喜喜地地守除酵節？</strong></p><p>猶大人歡喜地守除酵節，是因為耶和華（雅巍）使他們歡喜，<span>又感動亞述王的心轉向他們，堅固他們的手去完成重建神殿的工作。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15006022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:22",
          "end_ref": "15006022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 6:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571761,
    "reference_id": 124421,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯拉的職業是什麼？  </strong></p><p>他是一位精通摩西律法的文士。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:6",
          "end_ref": "15007006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571762,
    "reference_id": 124422,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼以斯拉能在從巴比倫到耶路撒冷的漫長旅途中平安抵達？  </strong></p><p>以斯拉能在從巴比倫到耶路撒冷的漫長旅途中平安抵達，是因為他的神的施恩的手保護著他。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:9",
          "end_ref": "15007009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571763,
    "reference_id": 124423,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>被允許與以斯拉一起歸回耶路撒冷的有哪些人？</strong></p><p>亞達薛西王下了一道<span>諭旨</span>，凡在他的國中有自願與以斯拉一同前往耶路撒冷的以色列人、祭司和利未人，都可以與以斯拉同行。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:13",
          "end_ref": "15007013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571764,
    "reference_id": 124424,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王和他的七位謀士為什麼差派以色列人回到耶路撒冷？  </strong></p><p>王和他的七位謀士差派以色列人回到耶路撒冷，是為了查看猶大和耶路撒冷的情況，並把他們甘心獻上的金銀以及在巴比倫全省所收集到的金銀都帶著，連同百姓們和祭司們甘心獻上的祭物，一同帶回耶路撒冷。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:14",
          "end_ref": "15007014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571765,
    "reference_id": 124425,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼王和他的七位謀士差以色列人回到耶路撒冷？</strong></p><p>王和他的七位謀士差以色列人回到耶路撒冷，<span>是為了查看猶大和耶路撒冷的情況，並將王與謀士們甘心獻上的金銀以及在巴比倫全省所得的金銀，連同百姓和祭司們甘心獻上的祭物，一同帶到耶路撒冷。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:16",
          "end_ref": "15007016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571766,
    "reference_id": 124426,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>猶太人要如何支付建造神的殿所需的額外物品？</strong></p><p>亞達薛西王下令，讓猶大人可以從王的府庫中，取用他們為建造神的殿所需的一切額外物品。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:20",
          "end_ref": "15007020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571767,
    "reference_id": 124427,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼亞達薛西說庫官應該完全按照天上之神對於聖殿的命令行事？</strong></p><p>亞達薛西王說庫官應該完全按照天上之神對於聖殿的命令行事，這樣神的憤怒就不會<span>臨到王和王眾子的國。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:23",
          "end_ref": "15007023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571768,
    "reference_id": 124428,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:26",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007026",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>亞達薛西王的法令規定，對於每一個不遵守以斯拉的神的律法以及王的命令的人，應該怎麼處置？</strong></p><p>亞達薛西下令，凡不遵守以斯拉的神的律法以及王的命令的人，應當被定罪，<span>或治死，或充軍，或抄家，或囚禁</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007026",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:26",
          "end_ref": "15007026",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:26"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571769,
    "reference_id": 124429,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 7:28",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15007028",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>是什麼使以斯拉得以剛強？  </strong></p><p>以斯拉知道耶和華（雅巍）——他神的手幫助了他，就得以剛強。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15007028",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:28",
          "end_ref": "15007028",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 7:28"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571770,
    "reference_id": 124430,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 8:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15008015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當以斯拉在流向亞哈瓦的河邊查看百姓和祭司時，發現缺少了什麼？</strong></p><p>當以斯拉在流向亞哈瓦的河邊查看百姓和祭司時，他找不到任何利未人的後裔。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
