  {
    "content_id": 571771,
    "reference_id": 124431,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 8:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15008017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼以斯拉派人去找易多和他的弟兄們？</strong></p><p>以斯拉派人去找易多和他的弟兄們，是<span>因為他希望易多和他的弟兄能差派利未人在神的殿服事。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15008017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:17",
          "end_ref": "15008017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:17"
        }
