    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571773,
    "reference_id": 124433,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 8:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15008022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>在前往耶路撒冷時，為什麼以斯拉沒有向王要求步兵或馬兵來保護猶大人免受敵人的攻擊？</strong></p><p>以斯拉在旅途中之所以沒有求王的步兵和馬兵，是因為<span>以斯拉羞於對王開口；因為他曾告訴過王，他們的神施恩的手必幫助一切尋求祂的；同時，祂的能力和忿怒必攻擊一切離棄祂的。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15008022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:22",
          "end_ref": "15008022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571774,
    "reference_id": 124434,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 8:29",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15008029",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>那十二個人要看守金銀多久？</strong></p><p>那十二個人要看守金銀，<span>直到在耶路撒冷耶和華（雅巍）殿的庫房裡，將金銀在祭司、利未人和以色列各族長面前秤量清楚為止。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15008029",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:29",
          "end_ref": "15008029",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:29"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571775,
    "reference_id": 124435,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 8:31",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15008031",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>當他們前往耶路撒冷時，以斯拉</strong><span><strong>如何描述</strong></span><strong>神的手在他和其餘的猶太人身上？</strong></p><p>以斯拉說神的手會在他們前往耶路撒冷時，在他和其餘的猶太人身上保護他們脫離敵人的手和埋伏。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15008031",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:31",
          "end_ref": "15008031",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:31"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571776,
    "reference_id": 124436,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 8:36",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15008036",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>王的諭旨是給誰的？</strong></p><p>王的<span>諭旨是給王的</span>總督和河西的省長的。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15008036",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 8:36",
          "end_ref": "15008036",
