    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571777,
    "reference_id": 124437,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 9:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15009002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以色列人在哪方面沒有與其他國的人民分別出來？</strong>  </p><p>以色列人沒有與其他國的人民分別出來，是因為他們娶了外邦女子，並且讓他們的兒子娶外邦女子為妻。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15009002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:2",
          "end_ref": "15009002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571778,
    "reference_id": 124438,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 9:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15009003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯拉對人民的不忠有何回應？</strong></p><p>以斯拉<span>撕裂了他的衣服和外袍，拔了頭髮和鬍鬚，驚懼憂悶而坐。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15009003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:3",
          "end_ref": "15009003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571779,
    "reference_id": 124439,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 9:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15009006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯拉因為什麼而感到抱愧蒙羞，不敢向耶和華（雅巍）仰面？  </strong></p><p>以斯拉之所以感到抱愧蒙羞，不敢向耶和華（雅巍）仰面，是因為他百姓的罪孽和過犯極其嚴重。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15009006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:6",
          "end_ref": "15009006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571780,
    "reference_id": 124440,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 9:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15009009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>神在猶大人努力建造神的殿時，賜給了他們什麼？  </strong></p><p>神在猶大人努力建造神的殿時，神延續了祂的盟約的信實給猶大人民。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15009009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:9",
          "end_ref": "15009009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571781,
    "reference_id": 124441,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 9:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15009012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>神為什麼不希望以色列人與當地人通婚？  </strong></p><p>神不希望以色列人與當地人通婚是因為這些人不潔的行為，以及他們做了神所憎惡的事，使這地變得污穢。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15009012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:12",
          "end_ref": "15009012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571782,
    "reference_id": 124442,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 9:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15009013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>神保留了什麼？</strong></p><p>儘管猶大人的罪孽應得審判，但神抑制祂自己，<span>沒有完全審判他們，而是憐憫他們，允許他們回到耶路撒冷並重建神的殿。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15009013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:13",
          "end_ref": "15009013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 9:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571783,
    "reference_id": 124443,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>以斯拉在禱告和認罪時做了什麼？</strong></p><p>以斯拉在禱告和認罪時，痛哭並<span>俯伏在神殿前</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:1",
          "end_ref": "15010001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571784,
    "reference_id": 124444,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>示迦尼說以色列人應該立什麼約？</strong></p><p>示迦尼說他們應該與他們的神立一個約，將所有外邦婦女和她們的孩子都送走。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:3",
          "end_ref": "15010003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571785,
    "reference_id": 124445,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼以斯拉不吃任何餅或喝任何水？</strong></p><p>以斯拉不吃任何餅或喝任何水，是因為哀悼被擄之人的不忠誠。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:6",
          "end_ref": "15010006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571786,
    "reference_id": 124446,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>若有以色列人三日之內不來到耶路撒冷，會發生什麼事？</strong></p><p>任何以色列人若在三日內不來到耶路撒冷，<span>就會被抄家，使他離開被擄歸回之人的會。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:8",
          "end_ref": "15010008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571787,
    "reference_id": 124447,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>是哪兩件事使站在神殿前空地的人們</strong><span><strong>戰兢</strong></span><strong>？</strong></p><p>所有站在神殿前空地的人因這件事和雨水而<span>戰兢</span>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:9",
          "end_ref": "15010009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571788,
    "reference_id": 124448,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為什麼以色列人想要有更多時間遣散外邦女子？</strong></p><p>以色列人想要有更多時間遣散外邦女子是<span>因為她們人數眾多，他們在這件事上已經犯了許多悖逆的行為，因此需要不止一兩天的時間來完成這個過程。而且當時正值雨季，他們也沒有足夠的力量站在戶外來完成這個過程。</span></p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:13",
          "end_ref": "15010013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571789,
    "reference_id": 124449,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>為了查明以色列男子娶外邦女子為妻的事，共花了多長時間？</strong></p><p>從第十個月的第一天到翌年正月的第一天，才完全查明此事。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:17",
          "end_ref": "15010017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 571790,
    "reference_id": 124450,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "以斯拉記 10:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "15010019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>那些娶了外邦女子為妻的以色列人做了什麼？</strong></p><p>有罪的以色列人承諾送走他們的外邦妻子，並為他們的罪獻上一隻公綿羊。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "15010019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:19",
          "end_ref": "15010019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "EZR 10:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  }
